headline: Harbor Capital Factor U.S. Large Cap ETF Q4 2024 Commentary
summary: During the fourth quarter, Harbor Human Capital Factor US Large Cap ETF returned 2.72%, (at NAV) slightly underperforming CIBC Human Capital Index, which returned 2.80%.
